      {
        "experiment_id": 1,
        "reaction_type": "氢化反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrogenation reaction",
        "description": "在ZnCrOₓ和MnZnCrOₓ氧化物上进行二甲醚（CH₃OCH₃）的氢化反应测试。MnZnCrOₓ表现出更强的氢化能力，二甲醚转化率更高（25%），甲烷选择性达89%。",
        "text_snippet": "the hydrogenation reactions of CH₃OCH₃ are tested over both oxides (Fig. S9). For ZnCrOₓ oxide, the CH₄ selectivity reaches 87% at a CH₃OCH₃ conversion of 10%... When it comes to MnZnCrOₓ, a much higher conversion of 25% and CH₄ selectivity of 89% are acquired due to its stronger hydrogenation ability.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "氢化反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrogenation reaction",
        "description": "在两种氧化物上进行乙烯（C₂H₄）的氢化反应测试，乙烯完全转化为乙烷（C₂H₆）。",
        "text_snippet": "the hydrogenation of a model alkene, C₂H₄, is also conducted, which is completely converted into C₂H₆ over both oxides (Fig. S10).",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 3,
        "reaction_type": "氢化反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrogenation reaction",
        "description": "在模拟反应气氛下进行合成气转化实验，将二甲醚与合成气的混合气体通过双床层配置（ZSM-5在上，氧化物在下）来研究反应环境对迭代加氢程度的影响。",
        "text_snippet": "the syngas conversion under a simulated reaction aero-environment is designed... the gas mixture of CH₃OCH₃ and syngas is adopted to pass a dual-bed configuration with ZSM-5 packed above oxides which is separated by quartz wool (Fig. 3b).",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
  },
